    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean with only minor cosmetic wear, such as a few small stone chips on the hood and light scratches near the door handles. Inside, the cabin is well-preserved with minor wear on the driver's seat bolster, but all electronics and features are fully functional. It drives smoothly and represents a reliable option for anyone looking for a solid, pre-owned car.",
